<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
	  tal:define="lang context/i18n:user_lang"
	  tal:attributes="lang lang; xml:lang lang;" i18n:domain="ztfy.sendit">
<head>
	<title i18n:translate="">[<span tal:content="context/i18n:mail_subject_header" i18n:name="header"></span>] Please confirm registration</title>
</head>
<body>
	<p i18n:translate="">Hello,</p>
	<p i18n:translate=""><tal:var content="context/i18n:mail_service_name" i18n:name="service_name" /> is a files sharing service provided by
		<tal:var content="context/i18n:mail_service_owner" i18n:name="service_owner" />.</p>
	<p i18n:translate="">Registration info was entered for your email address.</p>
	<p i18n:translate="">By activating this service, you will get the possibility to share (send and receive) packets with your contacts from
		<tal:var content="context/i18n:mail_service_owner" i18n:name="service_owner" />.</p>
	<p><span i18n:translate="">To confirm your registration, please click on the following link and re-enter your login credentials:</span><br />
		<a tal:define="href string:${context/@@absolute_url}/@@register_confirm.html?hash=${options/hash}"
		   tal:attributes="href href"
		   tal:content="href" />
	</p>
	<p i18n:translate="">If you don't want to confirm this registration, please just ignore this message and your registration information will be deleted within
		<tal:var content="context/confirmation_delay" i18n:name="confirmation_delay" /> days.</p>
	<p i18n:translate="">Thank you for using our services.</p>
	<div tal:content="structure context/i18n:mail_signature" />
</body>
</html>